The interior of the 2013 Hyundai Genesis RSpec
with its plush leather seating surfaces and

00:01:59.789 --> 00:02:05.220
rear heated seats help add to the comfort
of both the front and rear seat passengers.

00:02:05.220 --> 00:02:09.930
The Genesis central command is the steering
wheel with its cruise control, radio controls,

00:02:09.930 --> 00:02:16.340
smart cruise distance setting as well as buttons
allowing for display selection.

00:02:16.340 --> 00:02:22.069
The Genesis RSpec comes equipped with push
button start.

00:02:22.069 --> 00:02:27.900
Parking sensor control, lane departure warning,
Electronic Stability control auto hold and

00:02:27.900 --> 00:02:34.209
auto parking brake all controlled to the left
side of the steering wheel esily withing the

00:02:34.209 --> 00:02:41.450
drivers read.

00:02:41.450 --> 00:02:47.069
The driver has control of the Lexicon audio
system close by in the center console and

00:02:47.069 --> 00:02:53.500
up from that lies the a/c controls along with
the 8 inch navigation screen.

00:02:53.500 --> 00:03:00.310
Along with the gear shift lies the heat controls
for the passenger and the heating and cooling

00:03:00.310 --> 00:03:02.940
seat controls for the driver.

00:03:02.940 --> 00:03:06.069
Behind the gear shift lies the navigation
controls.

00:03:06.069 --> 00:03:12.269
The Genesis RSpec boasts an 8-inch screen
with turn-by-turn navigation, enhanced multimedia

00:03:12.269 --> 00:03:15.030
control, and a driver's information system.

00:03:15.030 --> 00:03:19.240
It also boasts an enhanced voice-recognition
system.

00:03:19.240 --> 00:03:27.519
Within this system lies a 64 GB solid state
hard drive with zero moving parts.

00:03:27.519 --> 00:03:29.129
Driver has 2 memory settings available.

00:03:29.129 --> 00:03:34.439
A rear automatic sunshade is standard on the
2013 Hyundai Genesis RSpec.

00:03:34.439 --> 00:03:39.080
Auto up and down windows on both the passenger
and drivers windows.

00:03:39.080 --> 00:03:43.970
Also on the driver door is the mirror controls
and power door locks.

00:03:43.970 --> 00:03:51.629
On the drivers side is 8 way power adjustable
seats with Lumbar.

00:03:51.629 --> 00:03:59.530
4 way power adjustable seats are standard
on the passenger side of the RSpec.

